snippet.title: Nell & the Festival of Spooks - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a slice-of-life visual novel about a seemingly ordinary girl named Nell, who has a love for horror. An eclipse transports her to a spooky town where she gets enrolled into a fancy academy.  

Download the game here: https://bekiwoo.itch.io/nell-the-festival-of-spooks ! 

It's a personal game project that I've been working on for the past year and was released on Haloween 2020. It's being showcased online at ComicsxGames on May 8, go check it out!

Follow me here: 
https://www.instagram.com/bekiwoo/
